          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where is He my Beloved?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Tell me where you have laid Him"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And I’ll carry Him away, I’ll carry Him away."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And then I heard a voice say, “Mary.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That sweetest voice that penetrated me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is the voice of my Beloved,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, my Love."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I have found my Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I have found my Beloved!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I have found Whom my soul doth love,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus, my love, I just love You!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But Jesus told me not to touch Him yet."
